10. WHAT ABOUT CHILDREN PRIVACY?
Minors below 16 years old cannot create a Game Account to connect to our Games.
Homa does not intentionally collect personal data from minors aged under 16. If we realize we have collected personal data regarding a minor within the meaning of the applicable data protection regulation, we will immediately delete it.
11. WHEN AND HOW WILL YOU BE INFORMED IF THIS POLICY CHANGES?
We periodically review this Policy to ensure it is compliant and up to date with applicable data protection regulation.
You will be notified in case of substantial changes to the Policy (for example, if the modifications impact the categories of personal data processed or the purposes of processing), and we will send you a hyperlink to the updated Privacy Policy within 30 days before publication. This information will be provided to you by email or will be made available via a pop-up window displayed when visiting our Websites. This will give you the opportunity to review the updated Policy before you decide whether to continue using our Services.
